Package ch.lambdaj.collection

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LambdaCollection<T>
    A collection that extends the collection interface with the fluent interface methods provided by lambdaj
    LambdaCollections
    This class consists exclusively of static methods that allow to create LambdaCollections.
    LambdaGroup<T>
    A wrapper of a group that returns LambdaLists instead of Lists in order to allow a fluent interface programming
    LambdaIterable<T>
    An Iterable that extends the Iterable interface with the fluent interface methods provided by lambdaj
    LambdaIterator<T>
    An Iterator that extends the Iterator interface with the fluent interface methods provided by lambdaj
    LambdaList<T>
    A List that extends the List interface with the fluent interface methods provided by lambdaj
    LambdaMap<K,V>
    A Map that extends the Map interface with the fluent interface methods provided by lambdaj
    LambdaSet<T>
    A Set that extends the Set interface with the fluent interface methods provided by lambdaj
